'''環蛸枕'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Linthia'''''}}），又名'''林西海膽'''，是一[[屬|屬]]已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[海膽|海膽]]。牠們生存於[[晚白堊紀|晚白堊紀]]至[[上新世|上新世]]。其[[化石|化石]]分佈在[[非洲|非洲]]、[[亞洲|亞洲]]、[[歐洲|歐洲]]、[[北美洲|北美洲]]及[[南美洲|南美洲]]。<ref>[http://paleodb.org/cgi-bin/bridge.pl?action=checkTaxonInfo&taxon_no=33417 ''Linthia''] {{Wayback|url=http://paleodb.org/cgi-bin/bridge.pl?action=checkTaxonInfo&taxon_no=33417 |date=20120328182443 }} in the [[Paleobiology_Database|Paleobiology Database]]</ref>

== 特徵 ==
環蛸枕是一種很小、緊密的[[心海膽|心海膽]]，在其前端有很突出的深凹口，線條分明的[[花瓣|花瓣]]狀步帶長有孔。頂盤上四個大[[生殖|生殖]]孔用於排放[[卵細胞|卵]]和[[精子|精子]]。牠們生活在鬆軟沉積的洞穴裡。<ref>{{cite book | title=自然珍藏系列──化石圖鑑 | location = [[台灣|台灣]][[新北市|新北市]] | publisher=[[貓頭鷹出版社|貓頭鷹出版社]] | author= Cyril Walker | author2= Davod Ward | authorlink=Cyril Walker (palaeontologist) | authorlink2=David Ward (palaeontologist) | series=自然珍藏系列 | year=2002 | page=183 | date = 2002-02 | language = zh-hant}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title=Fossils | url=https://archive.org/details/fossils0000walk_e1r0 | publisher=[[多林金德斯利|Dorling Kindersley]] | author=Walker, Cyril | last2=Ward | first2=David | authorlink=Cyril Walker (palaeontologist) | authorlink2=David Ward (palaeontologist) | series=Smithsonian Handbooks | year=2002 | page=[https://archive.org/details/fossils0000walk_e1r0/page/183 183] | isbn=0789489848 | edition=revised, illustrated}}</ref>

